mtcars %>%
  ggplot(aes(mpg, qsec)) + 
  stat_smooth(color = "darkorchid4", fill = "skyblue") + 
  geom_point(color = "black", shape = 3) + 
  theme_bw()

`geom_smooth()` using method = 'loess' and formula = 'y ~ x'
